instructions: Put the charger on the table
Put the dinner fork on the left hand side of the charger
Put the dinner knife on the right hand side of the charger
Put a salad fork on the left hand side on the dinner fork
put a salad knife on the right hand side of the dinner knife
put a soup spoon on the right hand side of the salad knife
Put a desert spoon above the charger laying horizontally
Put a dessert fork under the desert spoon laying horizontally
Put a bread plate above the charger on the left side of the dessert spoon and a dinner plate on the charger
put a butter knife on the bread plate
Put a water glass above the salad knife
Put a napkin on top of the charger and plate
